tox-libtoxcore-ngc

Sources: https://github.com/JFreegman/toxcore

# Prepare

Use new_groupchats.

# Compile

Arch         - use libsodium package from community repo
CentOS 6     - use yasm, autoconf268 and libconfig package from EPEL-6
CentOS 7     - use yasm package from EPEL-7
Ubuntu 12.04 - use libconfig package from separate tox backports repo
